  section.sg-sect#highlight-object
    h2 The Highlight Object
    p.
      Callouts on the home page or interior pages are Highlight Objects.
      Use a #[code section.o-Highlight] if the content belongs in a
      #[code &lt;main&gt;] element, or use an #[code aside.o-Highlight]
      if the content is a #[i &ldquo;callout&rdquo;] (not essential to the page content).
      The top-level heading of this Object should be a #[code h1.o-Highlight__Hn].
